description: Take the stress out of a busy night with this delicious stir-fry loaded with prawns and veggies that you can get on the table in 20 minutes.
name: Prawn & Leek Stir-fry Recipe | Woolworths

recipeInstructions.text: Add prawns and sauce and cook for 2-3 minutes or until prawns change colour. Serve sprinkled with sesame seeds.
